 class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\">Das <strong>HTML Element <code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></strong> zeichent einen Seitenbereich aus, der dazu bestimmt ist Navigationslinks bereitzustellen, die entweder zum aktuellen Dokument oder zu anderen Dokumenten zeigen. Häufige Beispiele für Navigationsbereiche sind Menüs, Inhaltsverzeichnisse oder andere Verzeichnisse.</span></p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\">Inhaltskategorien</a></th>\n   <td><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flie%c3%9fender_inhalt\">Fließender Inhalt</a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#unterteilender_inhalt\">Unterteilender Inhalt</a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#f%c3%bchlbarer_inhalt\">Fühlbarer Inhalt</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Erlaubter Inhalt</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flie%c3%9fender_inhalt\">Fließender Inhalt</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Tag Wegfall</th>\n   <td>Keine, sowohl das Anfangs- als auch das End-Tag sind erforderlich.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Erlaubte Elternelemente</th>\n   <td>Alle Elemente die <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flie%c3%9fender_inhalt\">fließenden Inhalt</a> akzeptieren.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Erlaubte ARIA-Rollen</th>\n   <td>Keine</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">DOM interface</th>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attribute","title":"Attribute","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieses Element besitzt nur die <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">globalen Attribute</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"verwendungshinweise","title":"Verwendungshinweise","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Es ist nicht nötig, dass alle Links in einen <code>&lt;nav&gt;</code> Element enthalten sind. Die Benutzung von <code>&lt;nav&gt;</code> ist nur für wichtige Abschnitte von Navigationslinks beabsichtigt; normalerweise enthält das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a> Element eine Liste von Links, welche nicht in einem <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a> Element beinhaltet sein müssen.</li>\n <li>Ein Dokument darf mehrere <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a> Elemente enthalten, zum Beispiel, eins für die Seitennavigation und eins für seiteninterne Navigation. <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-labelledby_attribute\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">aria-labelledby</a></code> kann benutzt werden um Barrierefreiheit zu fördern (siehe <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements#labeling_section_content\">Beispiel</a>).</li>\n <li>User-Agents, wie Bildschirmleser zur Unterstützung von Menschen mit Behinderung, können dieses Element benutzen, um zu entscheiden, ob das anfängliche Rendering von Navigationsinhalt ausgelassen werden kann.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In diesem Beispiel wird das <code>&lt;nav&gt;</code> Element benutzt, um eine ungeordnete Liste (<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a>) von Links. Mit entsprechenden CSS kann dies als Seitenleiste, Navigationsleiste oder Drop-Down-Menü verwendet werden.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>nav</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>menu<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Startseite<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Über<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Kontakt<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>nav</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Anmerkung</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/sections.html#the-nav-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;nav&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Keine Änderung seit dem letzten W3C Schnapschuss.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/sections.html#the-nav-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;nav&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Anfängliche Definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser-Kompatibilität","id":"browser-kompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.nav","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Other section-related elements: <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>;</li>\n <li class=\"last\"><a class=\"deki-ns current page-not-created\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Sections and outlines of an HTML5 document</a>.</li>\n <li class=\"last\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/navigation_role\">ARIA: Navigation role</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Attribute","id":"attribute"},{"text":"Verwendungshinweise","id":"verwendungshinweise"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"beispiel"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser-Kompatibilität","id":"browser-kompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Das HTML Element <nav> zeichent einen Seitenbereich aus, der dazu bestimmt ist Navigationslinks bereitzustellen, die entweder zum aktuellen Dokument oder zu anderen Dokumenten zeigen. Häufige Beispiele für Navigationsbereiche sind Menüs, Inhaltsverzeichnisse oder andere Verzeichnisse.","popularity":0.0006,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<nav>: The Navigation Section element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<nav>: El elemento de sección de navegación","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<nav> : l'élément de section de navigation","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<nav>: ナビゲーションセクション要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<nav>: 탐색 구획 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"nav","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Элемент секции навигации <nav>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<nav>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"<nav>","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/html/element/nav","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/html/element/nav/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: HyperText Markup Language"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav","title":"nav"}],"pageTitle":"nav - HTML: HyperText Markup Language | MDN","noIndexing":false}}